《'''一日一生'''》（{{Lang-en|''Life in a Day''}}）是一部即將上映的[[群眾外包|群眾外包]][[紀錄片|紀錄片]]，為2011紀錄片《{{link-en|一日一生 (2011年電影)|Life in a Day (2011 film)|一日一生}}》的續集，於2021年在[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]上首映，然後於2月7日在 [[YouTube|YouTube]] 上播出<ref>{{Cite web|title=Life In A Day 2020: How YOU can take part in new Life In A Day film|url=https://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/films/1307307/Life-In-A-Day-2020-How-to-take-part-Life-In-A-Day-film-date-ridley-scott|accessdate=|author=JENNY DESBOROUGH|date=2020-07-11|format=|work=Express.co.uk|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922180533/https://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/films/1307307/Life-In-A-Day-2020-How-to-take-part-Life-In-A-Day-film-date-ridley-scott}}</ref>。與之前的版本一樣，該紀錄片將包括一系列精選的畫面剪輯，且只記錄2020年7月25日這一天在世界上所發生的事。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Kevin Macdonald, Ridley Scott to Reunite for 'Life in a Day 2020,' 10 Years on From Crowdsourced Original|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kevin-macdonald-ridley-scott-working-life-day-2020-1302390|author=Alex Ritman|date=2020-07-08|format=|work=The Hollywood Reporter|publisher=|language=en|access-date=2020-07-21|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814134606/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kevin-macdonald-ridley-scott-working-life-day-2020-1302390}}</ref>知名台灣女Youtuber[[魚乾_(YouTuber)|魚乾]]也參與其中。<ref>{{youtube|2pFj59bqkwU|【魚乾】演唱會？《Life in a Day》我的一天！}}</ref><ref>{{youtube|vcsSc2iksC0|Life in a Day 2020|m=14|s=57}}</ref>

== 主題和製作 ==
電影的宣佈於7月8日在電影的YouTube頻道上發布<ref>{{Cite web|title=Make a movie with Ridley Scott and Kevin Macdonald {{!}} Film your day July 25 - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RfKP3EXVfX4|accessdate=2020-07-21|work=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2022-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325102345/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RfKP3EXVfX4}}</ref>，處在[[COVID-19大流行|COVID-19]]大流行、[[乔治·弗洛伊德之死引发的示威活动|弗洛伊德之死示威活動]]、很多[[自然灾害|自然災害]]的時機，[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]導演塔比莎·傑克遜（Tabitha Jackson）認為：「這是發布新作品的絕佳時機，該作品如此有力地展示了電影敘事的力量，以揭示和慶祝我們共同的人性。」<ref name=":0" />

